---
title: Goat Cheese & Pesto Spaghetti with Caramelised Cherry Tomatoes
description: The caramelised cherry tomatoes provide delicious bursts of sweet goodness as you tuck into this warming bowl of pasta. Hints of tangy goat cheese and buttery pine nuts add a touch of class and compliment the pesto perfectly, just as they should. Belissimo!
